<body>
<h2>What's New in 1.9.6</h2>  <ul><li><strong>More reliable widgets</strong> — widgets now refresh far more aggressively and stay much closer to the live app state.</li> <li><strong>Real widget refresh</strong> — the refresh action now performs an actual data fetch instead of just repainting cached values.</li> <li><strong>Smoother updates</strong> — valid Claude and Codex sessions now restore automatically after app updates, so the app is much less likely to show stale Connect states.</li></ul>
</body>
